st_remarks: A) Plot-8 is one of three ambient control plots in a larger experiment that included 12 plots in total, Plot-8 is located in Replicate Block 2, B) For select mature Pinon trees in Plot8, age is > 100+ years (determined from increment coring and tree ring analysis at root collar), C) stem density based on stems > 5.0 cm diameter (i.e., bole diameter or equivalent diameter if multi-stemmed), D) soil depth not determined at this time, but data should be available in late 2016
